    "text": "Natural Gas Tax Repeal Act\n\nThis bill eliminates a program administered by the Environmental Protection Agency that provides support for reducing methane emissions from the oil and gas sector. It also repeals a charge on methane emissions from\u00a0facilities that contain petroleum and natural gas systems and emit 25,000 metric tons or more of greenhouse gases per year."
